v1.0.5 (2021-01-07)
-------------------

* removed obsolete collections from output

* RF for follower collections is now displayed correctly

* added a detection for DOCUMENT in AQL, which may not find existing documents in
  one-shard databases.

* added a detection of unplanned failover canditates. Sometimes shards that are 
  already dropped stay in failoverCandidates


